    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "About Saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Priest Finds 'Whirring' Disc",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "In Yard and Holds It for FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Chicago, July 6 (U.P.).—A Catho-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "lic priest at Grafton, Wis., said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "tonight that a round, metal disc,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "which might be one of the myster-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "ious 'flying saucers,' had crashed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "into his parish yard and that he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "is holding it for the Federal",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Bureau of Investigation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "The Rev. Joseph Brasky of St.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Joseph's Church at Grafton, 45",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "miles north of Milwaukee, said he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "heard a swishing and whirring",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "noise this morning. A second later,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "he said, he heard a thud and a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "mild explosion.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "He investigated and found a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "sheet metal disc about 18 inches in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "diameter, resembling a circular",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "saw blade.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "\"The object still was warm,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "weighed about four or five pounds",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "and was about one eighth of an",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "inch thick,\" he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "There was a hole about one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "inch in diameter in the middle of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "the disc, he said, and in the open-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "ing were \"gadgets and some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "wires.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "The priest said he did not know",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "if his discovery were important,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "whether it might be an elab-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "orate practical joke. He said he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "had notified the FBI of his find.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "H. K. Johnson of the Milwaukee",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "FBI office said he hadn't heard",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "yet about the disc but that an offi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "cial report might be at his office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "The flying discs have been re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "ported \"seen\" by persons in 30",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "States, but Brasky's disc was the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "first one that actually had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "found—if that is what was found.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "His report came a few hours",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "after a military plane made an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "unsuccessful speed dash in an at-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "tempt to track down one of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "discs and the Army and scientists",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "sought to ascertain whether coast-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "to-coast reports about the discs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "zooming through the sky were fact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "or fancy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "Army planes scoured the north-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "west Pacific skies for them without",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "success today and one \"eyewitness\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "even reported having seen one of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "the discs take off in Arizona. A",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "St. Louis railroad man exhibited",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "some paper \"discs\" he said he had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "seen floating over St. Louis.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "The flying saucers which have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "been reported skimming through",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "America's skies at speeds up to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "1200 miles have eluded the usual-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "ly keen eye of radar.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "Capt. Tom Brown of the Army",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
